  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6838258c-54ea-40c6-b470-b616ba588c3f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-846553c7-8777-4bec-9633-b78a64ab2c5b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9ff084a7-188b-4e44-adc2-b5bd5d69c0f2\">안녕하세요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3bc040a0-e827-4ab7-9392-4812cdb756c4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-48d107dc-6fa2-4e58-8809-ab1d5fee5676\">남성역 이수한의원 문학진원장입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-201dccf2-b5c5-4dcc-ade5-5d48f7f247e4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e684ee25-76e3-4c86-8c34-a8966dc96f95\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-47e4beb9-02ef-4fa7-87c6-0c6d30c5049d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-597c66c5-e433-4200-8b89-1f5dcd2627e5\">등산으로 시작한 운동이 어찌어찌 우연한 기회들이 겹치면서 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a55f6eff-caa3-48f4-ae5c-25b1210067ad\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3f2c8e03-ec08-4b16-84ac-79f972b9642f\">마라톤까지 하게 되었네요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-399239a3-6924-4675-b5de-920dad68d361\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fd27c5cb-a614-47eb-8ee1-5f0239a7df3c\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8ad1cc87-0a53-4783-addd-d343e283e79c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d63df0c1-2fd3-4d9e-b3b6-0cbd0de97109\">그간 대회참가는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-875bfa61-2632-4540-a4e8-65bd52adc68d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ea38b177-a745-43c8-b870-66584eb4d9d1\">작년 9월 국제평화마라톤 10km</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-480072cd-b82c-4157-8595-a6f4b3efb050\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2384df58-0acb-4135-84f5-2f272f9c0cc1\">작년 11월 손기정마라톤 HALF (21km)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0e0d312d-ba76-4a7f-aa07-2b94173ec22c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c8e5e84b-2c11-4cb4-a0fd-2eae02090f15\">올 4월 서울하프마라톤 10km </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cb02d53d-8596-4ca7-87a9-79303214c74f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ab8f7407-8ff0-47d0-b504-b1f4cb93ecb1\">올 10월 서울레이스 HALF(21km)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a7575234-ad25-45fb-8e8b-f9bb37e1a0f3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9de9ae75-638f-47d4-b197-6d4ef65988c8\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a8823312-11b5-4173-be50-e57ebfd94724\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-56cfbe8a-ec8a-41a5-9145-8a4b50f57795\">이렇게 4번 완주했고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2ad852ac-2c0f-462e-9850-a9d56e1e7702\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2951a2e2-dcf1-4c71-8de9-d01dc7ab05f1\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-041e41f9-ceff-4b78-ad2b-c7e3ffb5b903\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-15e9972a-5139-4229-8724-1b95b7313ee5\">어제 드디어 대망의 풀코스(42.195km)에 도전했습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-deeebaaf-383a-499f-af92-7437259dc240\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-92f5c72c-51b9-4b8f-9380-37d5d4c991fe\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cb121fe7-0bcf-4e5a-a1a2-b5f7d5b442bb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4ea7890a-6298-423e-90e0-a75527ca6323\">풀코스는 준비없이 못한다는 말이 있어서. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f1370438-16f4-4eff-9082-50ee92a394f9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-30ad7063-ec5e-494c-baf2-f4e57b5fe2f9\">크고 작은 부상에 시달리면서 약 3개월간의 훈련 프로그램을 진행했어요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d8d348ab-cc95-47b7-913d-eb76e116e410\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2aabd43f-c3d2-44c5-97fa-bb6c7ceaafd4\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6954b87f-d600-4f51-b4ea-1be3ef017cbd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4f58aa88-c9a1-4f59-aacb-c3ab2436f418\">대회 날짜가 다가오면서 엄청난 긴장감에 시달리기도 하고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ef271d91-dfef-47c0-a194-9a86b048772c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-68a39a68-0b18-4b57-98d3-b36f0a320c18\">장거리 달리기를 하면 생기는 발목과 무릎의 통증을 덜어보고자</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bfadf95f-50d6-4f72-b8e2-69ed9633020f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4ce77004-25a3-4cd8-a6b5-045ba65bd4a2\">대회를 앞두고 체중 감량도 했습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fd84e781-2fc4-4d06-aa44-6497e0804119\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6aa37593-56f9-4b20-91ac-70b34532924e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-39da3343-830f-4ccb-b4e2-d34ba5e2002a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b6bb2428-3aba-42ff-b64d-0391af7ad0a0\">그러나.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f37f18dd-7280-4db3-b61c-11aabf4c536b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-60ae3d1a-9b94-4d46-ad8f-6e1a52ecdaab\">슬프게도 대회날 비예보. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0ee2a65b-e110-4e09-a39f-3a811dcbfbce\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-31736213-60bd-44ec-8748-43ee224a255a\">새벽에 일어났는데, 비가 세차게 내리더군요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b0be78c6-f043-4dfb-92af-eb764c15e4bc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8b5edb3e-f4ed-4a90-85dc-dc6c4261b695\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-34751553-0dda-4ab0-83d8-56fcff4cdf8d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-02f59148-402f-4d62-9dd8-c7127629fc6b\">우천시에도 대회는 정상적으로 진행된다는 알림 문자. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cdf54810-954e-4763-8e60-22c8d24fa0a0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a2ad354a-2fdc-4ece-965c-4fc563222dcd\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-80471c2e-4ee4-4f00-b5ff-5433ba74e56e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d7180be9-b6c9-4fe7-b931-0ea0d8489c17\">상반기에 대회 참가 신청을 하고, 몇 달간 훈련도 했으며, 몇 주간 생활관리 음식관리까지 했으니 대회는 무조건 참가한다고 맘 먹고 풀코스 출발지로 갔습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0cb3446b-aa88-4861-a85c-1f66d21ed3df\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-294365fb-f598-4eae-9cab-6e5ce9558861\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-76b09ba7-6b8a-4dde-b831-c6456b745758\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ba3b115e-4caa-461f-ab7f-b6dd11b50bbd\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c9031f08-d147-43b6-815e-f4fd9305098d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-70846472-35df-490d-8325-39c962b1f313\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0c4dad7d-638e-451c-a41f-fd1ef90a6a5c\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-0c4dad7d-638e-451