 SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-185e23bd-d8f2-40da-81e9-fc1e657b8124\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4265e2b8-f853-4304-ae72-453c12313545\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bf4c8c10-2b3c-432a-b382-f65412c0fe6a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-43650c8d-1cc4-4fda-9929-3fc01cbe215e\">... </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c385fd15-5912-4afa-bc7f-888496d8cf66\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cb45c6aa-f995-409f-9c0c-62d70cf5bbc9\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5dea7b80-c86b-4055-adb7-e186a472ef93\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d192fb49-81a5-4c1c-ab92-75126b56ab1e\">풀코스를 뛰는건 너무나 힘들었습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6503de8a-3df3-4376-81fd-a9462d790638\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d543df86-85d1-4e16-bde0-9274e088b87a\">출발할때는 비가 안왔는데, 중간부터 다시 비가 내려서 옷도 젖고, 신발도 젖고, 양말도 젖고 ㅜ.ㅠ </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c5c8bb90-36de-459a-96fb-c7756f171de4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7c2c85b4-7c2b-42c9-a658-9973a4aab189\">젖은 양말 때문에 발바닥에 물집이 잡혀서 뛰는 내내 아프고 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7874a1a9-ff3f-4c55-8d1e-a97cdba2bab4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-44186d1b-6dae-4f34-a4da-017d738393bb\">33km 넘어가면서 힘들고 춥고 아프고.. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-32573901-7e22-4796-8f3a-ab4c1257defa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cfcdede5-504c-47d8-9e0c-6cc8139e6c67\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-daca234a-8df3-4a34-aa3b-7bff4726d80d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8d0beacd-43d9-4e38-93a4-3cb931e8aefd\">제가 환자분 몇 분에게 풀코스 뛸거라고 말을 했거든요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-37ac5100-cbf6-4394-be6b-d085492981d1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9a4730e2-022a-425b-88f4-ca476d5462d1\">말하지 말 걸 그랬습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bf290f02-cdc1-4e24-a341-09139d5c9090\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-42551125-2732-4b3f-adbf-aaad694eb307\">가족들과 친구들에게는 &#x27;비와서 못뛰겠더라.. &#x27; 하면 되겠는데</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-420ac4de-1ef2-4d63-afd9-70bd496c1e89\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-63879169-d5f8-4394-8ee9-c61143778641\">환자분들에게는 차마 그렇게 말하지 못하겠어서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ec86ce9d-b366-4190-a32d-016269c5f5f2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-84cd23e1-9ccf-4d5a-a2ed-1e213843b3c7\">이 악물고 끝까지 뛰었습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d7441018-affa-4d1c-a97c-b1770cce09a1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-456d5945-bb53-4871-8827-ff7ca18fee67\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b480869d-306b-4066-8557-f35f79dbcf3d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-89541a0b-fcc0-44b9-bb61-75bf5b339656\">뭐.. 결과적으로 그 환자분들 덕분에 무사히 첫 풀코스를 완주했다고 봐야죠</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9d6a726f-cdd9-4ce7-a301-98f984910f5c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5f57bc52-2970-4377-816a-40488c9f79c3\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bc548b68-9ecd-4783-8642-71663e42fe40\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b8c2b263-a05d-44f0-829f-137f182c6cb7\">3시간 30분을 목표로 훈련을 했지만, 첫 풀코스 경험이고 + 비오는 날씨 때문에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-37e5405f-a4e7-4fed-b42c-89d710e17a7f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fdbdb9a5-cbc2-448e-873e-a0a1cd6f782d\">기록은 조금 늦었지만, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bb85a7ca-1d7e-4944-89f2-845932dfe759\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-690f650c-f8a6-436a-833f-934db727d160\">스스로 이정도면 잘 한거라고 칭찬 중입니다. ㅎㅎ</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e14f1812-e8f8-4e08-911a-03011a81163c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b45476ac-7045-47ca-a235-620ad2fc3126\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-33e95c53-4f2e-4e53-9e08-4d5336ebe88f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                      